#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:419
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "translation"
msgid "Alternate Translations"
msgstr "tradución"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each unit may have several <emphasis>alternate translations</emphasis> "
"associated with it. Such translations may appear during file update, when "
"the source string is slightly changed. In this case the old translation with "
"it's (old) source is moved to alternate translations list, so that they are "
"not lost."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When original text changes, gettext tools update translation files and "
#| "mark entries with changed original text as <emphasis>fuzzy</emphasis> (or "
#| "<emphasis>non-approved</emphasis> in other terminology). They store "
#| "previous original text so that translators could see what changes exactly "
#| "were made. &lokalize; simplifies life of translator and highlights parts "
#| "of original text that were changed in <guilabel>Original Diff</guilabel> "
#| "view."
msgid ""
"When translating software, usually gettext tools are used to prepare "
"translation files. When original text changes, gettext tools update "
"translation files and mark entries with changed original text as "
"<emphasis>fuzzy</emphasis> (or <emphasis>non-ready</emphasis> in other "
"terminology). They store previous original text so that translators could "
"see what changes exactly were made. &lokalize; simplifies the life of the "
"translator and highlights parts of the original text that were changed in "
"the <guilabel>Alternate Translations</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"Cando o texto orixe é modificado, as ferramentas de gettext anovan os "
"ficheiros de tradución e marcan as entradas ás que lles mudou o texto orixe "
"como <emphasis>dubidosa</emphasis> (con outros termos: <emphasis>non "
"aprobada</emphasis>). Tamén gardan o anterior texto orixe de tal xeito que "
"os tradutores poidan ver qué modificacións foron feitas. &lokalize; "
"simplifica a vida do tradutor e realza as partes do texto orixe que foron "
"modificadas na vista de <guilabel>Diferenzas co orixinal</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; highlighting parts of original text that were changed "
"since translation was last reviewed</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&lokalize; realza as partes do texto orixe que cambiaron desde a "
"última revisión da tradución</screeninfo>"

